!! Morphology

!! INTRODUCTION TO MORPHOLOGICAL ANALYSER OF VEPS


Multichar_Symbols
!! Multichar_symbols

!! The morphological analyses of wordforms of Veps are presented
!! in this system in terms of the following symbols.
!! (It is highly suggested to follow existing standards when adding new tags).

!! The parts-of-speech are:

 +N +A +Adv +V				  !!= @CODE@
 +Pron +CS +CC +Adp +Po +Pr   !!= @CODE@
 +Interj +Pcle +Num 		  !!= @CODE@

!! The parts of speech are further split up into:

 +Prop +Pers +Dem +Interr     !!= @CODE@
 +Refl +Recipr +Rel +Indef    !!= @CODE@


!! The Usage extents are marked using the following tags:

 +Use/Sub                     !!= @CODE@
 +Use/-Spell                  !!= @CODE@

!! The nominals are inflected in the following Case and Number

 +Sg +Pl							  !!= @CODE@
 +Nom +Acc +Gen  +Par 				  !!= @CODE@
 +Abl +Dat +Loc +Pros +Tra +Abe +Adc  !!= @CODE@
 +Ins +Apr +Ine +Ill +Ela +Egr		  !!= @CODE@
 +Prl +Ter1 +Ter2 +Ter3 +Add1 +Add2	  !!= @CODE@
 +Apr1 +Apr2						  !!= @CODE@
 +EssInst							  !!= @CODE@


!! The possession is marked as such:

 +PxSg1 +PxSg2 +PxSg3                 !!= @CODE@
 +PxPl1 +PxPl2 +PxPl3                 !!= @CODE@

!! The comparative forms are:

 +Comp +Superl                 !!= @CODE@

!! Numerals are classified under:

 +Attr +Card                !!= @CODE@
 +Ord 		                !!= @CODE@

!! Verb tense and moods are:

 +Prs +Prt 		            !!= @CODE@
 +Ind +Cond +Imprt          !!= @CODE@
 +Pos			            !!= @CODE@

!! Verb personal forms are:

 +ScSg1 +ScSg2 +ScSg3 +ScPl1 +ScPl2 +ScPl3   !!= @CODE@
 +RcSg1 +RcSg2 +RcSg3 +RcPl1 +RcPl2 +RcPl3   !!= @CODE@
 +RcSg +RcPl +ScSg +ScPl				     !!= @CODE@

!! Other verb forms are

 +Inf +Ger +Neg                 !!= @CODE@
 +ConNeg +ConNegII              !!= @CODE@
 +ImprtII 		                !!= @CODE@
 +PrsPrc +PrfPrc                !!= @CODE@
 +Sup +VGen +VAbess             !!= @CODE@

!! Abbreviated words are classified with:

 +ABBR +ACR   !!= @CODE@

!! Special symbols are classified with:

+CLB +PUNCT +LEFT +RIGHT !!= @CODE@

!! The verbs are syntactically split according to transitivity:

 +TV +IV  !!= @CODE@

!! Special multiword units are analysed with:

 +Multi !!= @CODE@

!! Non-dictionary words can be recognised with:

 +Guess  !!= @CODE@


!! Question and Focus particles:

 +Qst +Foc       !!= @CODE@
+Clt	         !!= @CODE@
+Foc/ki	         !!= @CODE@
+Foc/žo	         !!= @CODE@

+Appr	         !!= @CODE@
+Advc	         !!= @CODE@
+Ter	         !!= @CODE@
+Pro	         !!= @CODE@
+Car 	         !!= @CODE@

+PstI	         !!= @CODE@
+PstII	         !!= @CODE@



!! Semantics are classified with
 +Mal +Fem +Sur    !!= @CODE@
 +Plc 			   !!= @CODE@
 +Org			   !!= @CODE@
 +Obj			   !!= @CODE@
 +Ani			   !!= @CODE@
 +Hum			   !!= @CODE@
 +Plant			   !!= @CODE@
 +Group			   !!= @CODE@
 +Time 			   !!= @CODE@
 +Txt			   !!= @CODE@
 +Route			   !!= @CODE@
 +Measr 		   !!= @CODE@
 +Wthr			   !!= @CODE@
 +Build 		   !!= @CODE@
 +Edu			   !!= @CODE@
 +Veh			   !!= @CODE@
 +Clth			   !!= @CODE@


!! Derivations are classified under the morphophonetic form of the suffix, the
!! source and target part-of-speech.
 +V→N +V→V +V→A     !!= @CODE@
+Der/Ta		        !!= @CODE@
+Der/Te		        !!= @CODE@
+Der/ma		        !!= @CODE@
+Der/Tu		        !!= @CODE@
+Der/IA		        !!= @CODE@



